import React from 'react'
import { Navbar, Nav, Container } from 'react-bootstrap';

export default function index() {
  return (
    <Navbar bg="light" expand="lg" sticky='top' navbarScroll>
      <Container>
        <Navbar.Brand >React-Bootstrap</Navbar.Brand>
        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="navbarScroll" />
        <Navbar.Collapse id="navbarScroll">
          <Nav className="me-auto" >
            <Nav.Link href='#home'>Introduction</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="#link">Link</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="#projects">Project</Nav.Link>
            {/* <Link to="introduction" spy={true} smooth={true} offset={50}>Introduction</Link>
            <Link to="projects" spy={true} smooth={true} offset={50}>Home</Link> */}

          </Nav>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
  )
}
